{"tid":636384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[其實毒撚] 有冇人有拖拍但想自己一個","createTime":"2018-04-20T19:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T19:56:10.000Z","uid":104544,"like":65,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3610d8ac195e7043e365484b983b569824e64730","tid":636384,"uid":104544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T19:47:44.000Z","msg":"第一次出 post，希望唔好咁快沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為真係好苦惱<br />\n<br />\n今年 final year, 好多野做好多野煩，依家 sem 尾啲野湧住黎好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我同男朋友見得好密，佢係癡身果類黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我趕緊做野就會寧願仲係單身，<br />\n自己一個既話想點就點，<br />\n唔駛特登趕去食飯，想幾時食就幾時食<br />\n眾所週知自己食飯快手快腳好多，可以hea少啲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時做緊野又要抽時間講下電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣根本專心唔到<br />\n<br />\n係咪我有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係太大壓力，過左就冇事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多多藉口，根本唔值得有人愛"},{"pid":"c08321519e657c0e86e4aab6af85c2160e6005f2","tid":636384,"uid":7559,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T19:51:14.000Z","msg":"好明你嘅感受 我自己都係一個痴身嘅人<br />\n<br />\n但係如果你係愛佢 就會想搵佢 我明學業要用你好多時間 要覆message傾電話會晒好多時間 <br />\n<br />\n最好同佢傾下 每日可能定呢15-30分鐘同佢專心傾計 其他時間就忙返自己野 等佢明白你唔理佢係因為你忙緊 等佢可以安心"},{"pid":"f9b8771cadfc63a199b8e3fec4a359ca1df7e709","tid":636384,"uid":58663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:00:12.000Z","msg":"完全明白 近排sem尾已經夠忙 <br />\n想女朋友體諒下 呢排比多啲時間<br />\n過埋exam日日陪佢都得 <br />\n利申 拍拖到依家晚晚傾電話傾到訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45282ae02fea4a47d560db4c3ba616c64b4d820","tid":636384,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:07:34.000Z","msg":"已沉"},{"pid":"6b1548cdf7a63eff466cd77654311c30caa5e6ed","tid":636384,"uid":14618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:40:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8fbe1d4db0c17645b2c4a06a2aa17c8d02e956d","tid":636384,"uid":144295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9b8771cadfc63a199b8e3fec4a359ca1df7e709","tid":636384,"uid":58663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:00:12.000Z","msg":"完全明白 近排sem尾已經夠忙 <br />\n想女朋友體諒下 呢排比多啲時間<br />\n過埋exam日日陪佢都得 <br />\n利申 拍拖到依家晚晚傾電話傾到訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T21:04:35.000Z","msg":"拍咗幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5682800876db218798d75b4d5fbcf86d28b0af4b","tid":636384,"uid":61712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"我同個男仔岩岩開始<br />\n已經想變單身 覺得單身好似自由啲 <br />\n我呢種心態真係好想改變下"},{"pid":"b13bd239c3c97fea9ec3d4bfaa0c09f0bdacd58c","tid":636384,"uid":20696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:33:23.000Z","msg":"咁其實...有時忙起上嚟<br />\n我會都諗如果今晚無約男朋友食飯<br />\n我就有多啲時間做assignment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想要多啲時間係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但多到覺得寧願無佢我覺得過份咗<br />\n如果係我應該會覺得有啲傷心同心寒<br />\n拍拖帶俾你嘅野點止係見面食飯<br />\n因為呢啲野就否定佢存在好慘姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且見佢其實都係為自己叉叉電姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忙完就無野咖喇  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237312fd99a5d94292e3f4d333b3ddf93aa34153","tid":636384,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:41:00.000Z","msg":"點忙法 忙緊乜唔講<br />\n有幾痴身唔講 <br />\n好易炒車<br />\n<br />\n觀望下先"},{"pid":"df515450a735e68c2a92294da99a17181a42d6b2","tid":636384,"uid":104544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9b8771cadfc63a199b8e3fec4a359ca1df7e709","tid":636384,"uid":58663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:00:12.000Z","msg":"完全明白 近排sem尾已經夠忙 <br />\n想女朋友體諒下 呢排比多啲時間<br />\n過埋exam日日陪佢都得 <br />\n利申 拍拖到依家晚晚傾電話傾到訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T01:49:14.000Z","msg":"我地又係，<br />\n上年暑假，佢要番 intern 唔可以日日見<br />\n就會晚晚打電話比我，<br />\n都冇咁多野講，但就係要夾硬 hold 住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打加油捱埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6d562699dfe1d309f81c9533d0fa980ff3ce95","tid":636384,"uid":104544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5682800876db218798d75b4d5fbcf86d28b0af4b","tid":636384,"uid":61712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"我同個男仔岩岩開始<br />\n已經想變單身 覺得單身好似自由啲 <br />\n我呢種心態真係好想改變下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T01:55:25.000Z","msg":"絲打之前拍過拖未？"},{"pid":"060ab69fff6a9ad3d3db1b2433757a7f2fcb8df0","tid":636384,"uid":104544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"237312fd99a5d94292e3f4d333b3ddf93aa34153","tid":636384,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:41:00.000Z","msg":"點忙法 忙緊乜唔講<br />\n有幾痴身唔講 <br />\n好易炒車<br />\n<br />\n觀望下先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T02:15:13.000Z","msg":"簡單講，我 FYP 係要做 lab 果啲既（真係實驗，唔係電腦），lab 呢樣野好哂時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲 lab 唔係話完就完，開始左就好難暫停，講緊一樣野起碼要連做兩日，朝早做到晚咁樣，有時一個 step 錯左又要再做，又唔係包有 result，係靠做多幾次 bug fix 咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有其他科要 final 要寫 paper 果啲，都唔駛多講<br />\n<br />\n男朋友自己都有宿位，但佢每晚會走黎同我訓，咁自然午餐晚餐都係同佢<br />\n除左星期六日都見住（依家忙緊直頭屋企都冇番，日日見）冇見既話會打電話，但佢又唔收線，我又唔好意思停佢，好似我嫌佢煩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00c4e170ff504e18214f51e3155ff6e3249cf9f","tid":636384,"uid":149151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4f14cb8e32b815cbf321fb8c69d51d46bc065df","tid":636384,"uid":147276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T02:37:32.000Z","msg":"係呀 單身享受既其實唔係講緊瘋狂溝女<br />\n係講緊 可以自己決定大部分要做既野<br />\n訓教唔洗晚晚傾電話想訓就訓 <br />\n出街唔洗同人報到想去就去幾點返就幾點返 <br />\n雖然依家拍拖好開心 但有時真係會有想單身既feel"},{"pid":"c863afff19df701a2384480b345575ff3526c9e2","tid":636384,"uid":58663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b8fbe1d4db0c17645b2c4a06a2aa17c8d02e956d","tid":636384,"uid":144295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9b8771cadfc63a199b8e3fec4a359ca1df7e709","tid":636384,"uid":58663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:00:12.000Z","msg":"完全明白 近排sem尾已經夠忙 <br />\n想女朋友體諒下 呢排比多啲時間<br />\n過埋exam日日陪佢都得 <br />\n利申 拍拖到依家晚晚傾電話傾到訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T21:04:35.000Z","msg":"拍咗幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"2年幾"},{"pid":"151bb18650574ef714cda62923b97bbc7d34731d","tid":636384,"uid":144295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c863afff19df701a2384480b345575ff3526c9e2","tid":636384,"uid":58663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b8fbe1d4d